Key Findings:
Different crystallization rates or doping of germanium, carbon and other elements in poly-Si can change the band gap of poly-Si, which has an impact on the efficiency ( E
ff
) of TOPCon solar cells. The simulated band diagram, charge carrier concentration and recombination rate were used to deeply explore the defect in poly-Si and the influence of poly-Si with different band gap on the performance of TOPCon solar cells.
